You are designing the complete Figma prototype for MAGRO — a Mali AgriTech mobile app (+ web admin dashboard) that connects farmers and buyers. The app has 3 completely separate interfaces: Farmer, Buyer, and Admin. Each user sees only their own interface after login.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
🎨 PART 1 — DESIGN SYSTEM (apply to ALL screens)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

COLORS:
- Primary Green: #2E7D32
- Primary Orange: #F57C00
- Light Green (surface): #E8F5E9
- Light Orange (surface): #FFF3E0
- Background: #FAFAFA
- Card: #FFFFFF
- Text primary: #1A1A1A
- Text secondary: #757575
- Border: #E0E0E0
- Error: #D32F2F
- Success: #388E3C

TYPOGRAPHY: Inter / Noto Sans
- H1: 24px Bold | H2: 20px SemiBold | H3: 16px SemiBold
- Body: 14px Regular | Caption: 12px Regular | Button: 16px SemiBold

COMPONENTS (reuse across all screens):
- Primary button: orange #F57C00, full width, 56px height, 12px radius
- Secondary button: green #2E7D32 outline
- Ghost button: text only, no border
- Input field: 56px height, border #E0E0E0, active border #2E7D32, 8px radius
- OTP input: 6 boxes, 48x56px each, 8px radius, bold center text
- Badges: 🟡 Gold (≥80/100) | ⚪ Silver (60–79/100) | 🟢 Green (identity verified)
- Status chips: pending=orange | confirmed=blue | in_production=purple | ready=teal | delivered=green | cancelled=gray | disputed=red
- Card: white, 12px radius, shadow 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
- Bottom nav bar: 5 tabs, active tab colored (green for farmer, orange for buyer)
- Top app bar: back arrow + title + optional right icon
- Avatar: circle with initials fallback
- Star rating: 5 stars component
- Progress steps: horizontal stepper for onboarding
- Toast: success/error/warning banners
- FAB: orange circle, + icon, bottom right

LOGO: "MAGRO 🥭" — flat design, no shadow, no 3D, no gradient. Primary text in #2E7D32. Mango emoji inline. Clean, centered, minimal.

STYLE: Clean, modern, accessible. Large touch targets (min 48px). High contrast. Designed for low-tech users in rural Mali.

