🖥️ PART 8 — ADMIN WEB DASHBOARD (desktop layout)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Layout: Left sidebar (240px) + main content area. Desktop/tablet. 3 roles: Super Admin (full access), Moderator (disputes + accounts), Analyst (read-only stats).

SCREEN ADM1 — ADMIN LOGIN
- Centered card on dark green background
- MAGRO logo white
- Email + password inputs
- "Se connecter" green button
- Role-based auto-redirect after login

SCREEN ADM2 — SUPER ADMIN DASHBOARD
LEFT SIDEBAR:
  MAGRO logo | Divider
  📊 Vue d'ensemble (active)
  ⚖️ Litiges [badge: 7]
  👥 Vérifications [badge: 12]
  🏅 Experts MAGRO
  📈 Statistiques
  📤 Exports
  🔑 Clés API institutionnelles
  ⚙️ Paramètres
  (Super Admin only section:) 🔴 Sanctions sévères

MAIN AREA — KPI cards row:
  "Transactions aujourd'hui: 4 250 000 FCFA" (green)
  "Commandes en cours: 143" (blue)
  "Litiges ouverts: 7" (red if >5)
  "Utilisateurs actifs: 312" (purple)
  "Revenus MAGRO: 212 500 FCFA" (orange)

Recent activity feed below KPIs

SCREEN ADM3 — DISPUTES KANBAN
- Kanban board, 5 columns with horizontal scroll:
  🆕 Nouveau | 🔍 En instruction | ⏳ Preuves attendues | 🔄 Ré-inspection | ✅ Résolu

Each dispute card:
  Dispute ID | Amount in FCFA (bold red if >1 000 000 FCFA) | Farmer vs Buyer names | Days open counter | Certification badge if relevant | Assigned moderator avatar (or "Non assigné" tag)

Dispute detail RIGHT PANEL (slide in on click):
  Full timeline (order history + dispute events)
  Evidence section: 2 columns — Preuves agriculteur | Preuves acheteur (photo thumbnails + text)
  Certification report link (if product was certified)
  Decision panel:
    Label: "Rendre une décision"
    Radio options:
      ✅ Libération totale (100% → farmer)
      🔄 Remboursement total (100% → buyer)
      ⚖️ Split — ratio slider [Agriculteur: 70% ↔ Acheteur: 30%]
      🔍 Ré-inspection (recall expert)
      📦 Remboursement partiel
    Decision note text area (required)
    "Confirmer la décision" button — grayed out if amount >1M and user is Moderator (shows "Requiert Super Admin")

SCREEN ADM4 — VERIFICATION QUEUE
- Title: "Dossiers de vérification"
- Filter bar: All | Agriculteur | Acheteur | Coopérative | Expert | Industrie | Status: En attente / En revue / Approuvé / Rejeté
- Table columns: Name | Profile type | Region | Submitted date | Documents | Status chip | Actions
- Row expand → shows uploaded documents (thumbnails) + notes field
- Actions per row: "Approuver ✓" green | "Rejeter ✗" red (opens modal requiring rejection reason text)
- Warning banner at top: "⚠️ 3 dossiers en attente depuis plus de 5 jours ouvrés" (red)

SCREEN ADM5 — EXPERTS DASHBOARD
- Title: "Experts MAGRO"
- Expert cards grid (or table with expandable rows):
  Expert name + photo | Region(s) | Crop specialties | Certifications this month / total | Avg score given | Contestation rate % (red badge if >20%) | Revenue generated | Status: Active / Suspended
- Actions: "Voir le détail" | "Suspendre" (red) | "Définir zones d'intervention"
- Top warning: "⚠️ 1 expert avec taux de contestation > 20% — Revue obligatoire"

SCREEN ADM6 — STATISTICS (3 tabs)
TAB 1 — Opérationnel:
  Line chart: transaction volume over time (selectable: 7j / 30j / 6m / 1an)
  Bar chart: orders by status distribution
  Gauge meter: "Taux résolution litiges: 87%" (green if >80%)
  Pie chart: revenue breakdown (commissions / certifications / abonnements)

TAB 2 — Qualité:
  Stacked bar: badge distribution by region (Gold/Silver/Green)
  Line chart: avg certification score trend
  Horizontal bar: delivery rate by region
  Table: Top 10 certified crops

TAB 3 — Croissance:
  Line chart: new users per week (two lines: farmers vs buyers)
  Metric card: retention rate
  Bar chart: avg order value by buyer type (Particulier / Commerçant / Restaurateur / Institution / Industrie)
  Table: Top 10 farmers by total volume sold

SCREEN ADM7 — EXPORT & API KEYS
- Title: "Exports institutionnels & Clés API"
- API Keys table: Partner name | Quota/day | Last used | Status active/revoked | Created by | Actions (Activate / Revoke) — Super Admin only
- "Créer une nouvelle clé API" green button (Super Admin only)
- Export section:
  Preset options as cards:
    📊 Évolution des prix par culture/région
    🏅 Scores de certification agrégés
    📦 Volumes de production par saison
    🗺️ Flux commerciaux anonymisés
  Date range picker + Region filter
  Format: CSV / JSON toggle
  "Générer l'export" orange button
- Note: "Toutes les données exportées sont anonymisées — aucune donnée nominative"

