Frame size: 390x844px for all mobile screens (iPhone 14 standard).
Admin dashboard: 1440x900px (desktop).
Connect screens with Figma prototype arrows to show complete user flows.
Label each frame clearly with its screen code (e.g. "F3 — Create Listing").

Mobile screens: Green #2E7D32 primary for Farmer, Orange #F57C00 primary for Buyer.
Admin: Green sidebar, white content area, orange CTAs.
All designs: flat, clean, accessible, high contrast. Zero shadows on logo. Zero 3D effects. Designed for users in rural Mali with large touch targets.